data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. "GREAT BONES" throughout this hidden gem sitting on just under a half acre of land! The sellers loved it so much when they rented that they bought it, and it’s been kept immaculate ever since!! The upgraded architectural shingled roof is only 8 years old, you’ll have seamless gutters along the perimeter, an anchored shed (12ft x 30ft) with a wood floor, and the A/C was replaced in 2017. Now step inside to find STAINLESS STEEL appliances, wood-burning fireplace, epoxy floored garage, and space for ALL YOUR TOYS in the giant sized room (44ft x 38ft) with two extra bonus areas that can be used as creative spaces, library areas, offices, you name it! If that's not enough, there's also a small media room that can be soundproofed for recordings, used as a darkroom, or whatever your heart desires! Did I mention the entire home is pre-wired for surround sound and speakers? The possibilities are endless here – all you need to bring is your imagination and a preferred paint color - this home is waiting for your personal touch!
